snippet.title: AMBER HEARD Joins SAMS on a Humanitarian Mission to Lebanon 2019
snippet.description:
AMBER HEARD Joins SAMS on a Humanitarian Mission to Lebanon 2019
A short video when AMBER HEARD joined SAMS NGO mission in Lebanon. Aquaman Hollywood star Amber Hear is SAMS' Ambassador, visited the Syrian Refugees' camps for a Humanitarian Medical Mission.
Filmed and Edited by: Stephanie Kabalan

#AmberHeard #Lebanon #Hollywood 
#HumanRights #Refugees
